{"tid":521732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【娘娘辱兵】睇準犯賤男怪癖 「女王」靠羞辱男人年賺百萬","createTime":"2018-01-06T21:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T05:15:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"86afd2944b27cf4f0ea0d1db6feec803bae7a9f2","tid":521732,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T21:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180106/large/1515227514_78c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180106%2Flarge%2F1515227514_78c7.jpg&h=7e912b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國紐約一名女子靠「收兵」及在網上羞辱男人，一年可賺20萬美元（約156萬港元），有人更會為她購買名車、手袋及提供豪華旅行使費。她自豪地表示：「這不是威迫或勒索，他們自願給我想要的。」<br />\n<br />\n自稱「公主」的30歲梅格斯（'Princess Meggerz'），在2007年還是學生時就在網上「收兵」，由對方出錢讓她去晚飯夜蒲甚至旅行，她亦在網上列出想要的禮物清單，不時都收到豪爽的客人送禮，收過最貴重的一份禮物是價值7萬美元（約55萬港元）的寶馬M3跑車。她稱縱使是與男友人出行，有人仍會出錢讓他倆去土耳其、德國甚至埃及度假；另有一人就包辦她與女友人去希臘的使費。<br />\n她表示要做的就是與客人在網上聊天，不時羞辱一下他們，「每個人都有自己的癖好或幻想，對他們來說就是喜歡給錢女人花&hellip;&hellip;這可讓他們變興奮，我覺得有些男人就是想得到「女王」的認同，他們喜歡那份優越感。有些人喜歡在外出或晚飯時為我埋單，所以我和朋友們都得到不少好處。我的『兵仔』喜歡我展示他們送的禮物。」<br />\n梅格斯稱最風光時收入可達5萬美元（39萬港元），客人有老有嫩，「有人不算很富有，有人就是百萬富翁。他們每星期或每月給我錢，我會設個額度看他們是否付得起。」她亦不避忌靠這種方式賺錢，更會與他人分享「收兵」心得，「我不會隱瞞我所做的，我跟不少人分享過，有些女友人也想學一下。家人也知道我在做甚麼，但沒有問及詳情，只要我安全就好，反而與朋友說得最多。」<br />\n雖然有可觀的收入，但梅格斯沒有過度揮霍，反而會投資物業，如今已手持3個物業。她也稱當「女王」也有難處，除了應付自己正常的工作外，也要全天候候命隨時與「士兵」聊天，「我也是很負責任的，有時他們說我要得太多時，我就不會強求他們給錢我花，我不想毀掉任何人。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180107/57673291\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180107%2F57673291&d=blCoIAICFQIi7UBPh56t%2FzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=3c648bbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180107%2F57673291&h=816a233b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180107/57673291</a>"},{"pid":"bdf280657a6f551fc6e97b6b0108aeb2fff1738d","tid":521732,"uid":108022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T21:03:48.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"4e21c7fa62c1b5df1fb567fc973ba96e6eeb9079","tid":521732,"uid":2607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T21:06:52.000Z","msg":"蓋清與yoyo"},{"pid":"07d0948f180d26886718342e15273fcbdb6ca4cd","tid":521732,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T03:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45260bd48b753e6c4b8ef79b60ca73b5adec5a69","tid":521732,"uid":65587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T03:46:53.000Z","msg":"Yoyo"},{"pid":"f9bdb00f95501d789743f0edbe25fad5a69dd142","tid":521732,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf9c702dfcaea3898fda4d5cb4832720ff815b0","tid":521732,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:54:37.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  被女王調教"},{"pid":"c33057e310dcabf49c209525ef469ad15245076e","tid":521732,"uid":132847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:59:52.000Z","msg":"男女平等"},{"pid":"b98e502fe760d154aa85fe1c876e8bc3b911f944","tid":521732,"uid":119610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:00:11.000Z","msg":"wonder rabbitgirl <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7dded8f8a2a999a8a09629d2e085d32a0a79c6","tid":521732,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7afff8e3f6a80496dd85d345bde6e793dabe1f","tid":521732,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:11:02.000Z","msg":"咁多M男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26906f6432d07149192d9efa4010c9e0280b1bb","tid":521732,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}